    "long_instructions": "### Up & Down Remix\r\n\r\n**Define:** You've been hired to add effects to this remix of Up and Down by the Chainsmokers and 347aidan. Your requirements are:\r\n- The beat, bass, and guitar part must sound the same every time\r\n- The vocal and synth combinations must sound different each time\r\n\r\nYou will only need to add blocks between the `play together` blocks - the rest of the song is locked!\r\n\r\n**Prepare:** Plan what you want the beat, bass, and guitar section to sound like. Plan what you want the vocal and synth to sound like each time\r\n\r\n**Try:** Code your song! Listen to the example for an idea of what it could sound like!\r\n<div style=\"background:#ebe8f1; border: 0; border-radius: 10px; clear:both; padding: 5px\">\r\n\r\nNeed some help? Try the [<i class=\"fa-solid fa-book\"></i> Docs](#clickable=documentation-button) in the upper-right corner!\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n**Reflect:** Make sure your code has:\r\n\r\n- At least 6 effect blocks",
